GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Narrative_TranscriptBootstrappingUnderplayed> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Narrative_TranscriptBootstrappingUnderplayed> a narr:Digest ;
